==Finnish==
===Etymology===
From {{inh|fi|fiu-fin-pro|*üdin||bone marrow}} (compare {{cog|et|üdi}}, {{cog|krl|yjin}}), from {{inh|fi|fiu-pro|*wideme||bone marrow}} (compare {{cog|se|ađa||(bone with) marrow}}, {{cog|myv|удем||marrow; intellect}}, {{cog|chm|вем||marrow}}, {{cog|hu|velő||marrow}}).
